LLM Wiki WebUI

This project is a separate, non-invasive WebUI for a running native LLM Wiki
desktop application. It communicates with LLM Wiki through the local HTTP API
and does not modify the upstream application.

This project adapts API contract ideas, workbench interaction patterns,
Logo assets, and GPLv3-compatible implementation concepts from:

